text: Baltayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Karamaly-Gubeyevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 377 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Tuymazy, 16 km from Karamaly-Gubeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Baltayevo
